| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4576 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b2c59b89-4809-59c5-a7c2-839ee28042ce"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
